        "content": "\n# üì∞ Automated Daily News to Audio Newsletter.\n\n### üéØ What This Does\nTransforms daily news headlines into personalized audio newsletters automatically:\n‚Ä¢ **Fetches latest news** from NewsAPI on schedule\n‚Ä¢ **AI content creation** rewrites articles into newsletter format using Claude\n‚Ä¢ **Script generation** creates 2-minute audio-ready scripts with GPT-4\n‚Ä¢ **Text-to-speech** converts scripts to high-quality audio using OpenAI\n‚Ä¢ **Email delivery** sends audio newsletters as attachments\n\n### ‚ö° How It Works\n1. Scheduled trigger runs daily (customizable timing)\n2. Fetches top US headlines from NewsAPI\n3. Claude AI rewrites each article for newsletter format\n4. GPT-4 creates cohesive 2-minute audio script\n5. OpenAI converts text to natural-sounding speech\n6. Audio newsletter emailed to subscribers automatically\n\n### üõ†Ô∏è Setup Required\n**Before using this workflow:**\n1. Get NewsAPI key and replace `YOUR_NEWSAPI_KEY`\n2. Configure OpenRouter credentials for Claude access  \n3. Add OpenAI API key for text-to-speech\n4. Update recipient email address\n5. Customize news sources and AI prompts\n6. Test audio quality and email delivery\n\n### üí° Perfect For\n‚Ä¢ Content creators building audio-first content\n‚Ä¢ Busy professionals wanting daily news briefings\n‚Ä¢ Podcasters creating automated content segments  \n‚Ä¢ Teams needing internal news updates\n‚Ä¢ Anyone interested in AI-powered media automation"
